{"tid":2463646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國的秘密營地 消失的新疆維吾爾人都遭遇了什麼？","createTime":"2021-03-27T01:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T02:46:19.000Z","uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d11edb82ac2c531de44ce7a78df07e9b851be4b4","tid":2463646,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:13:55.000Z","msg":"2015年7月12日，一顆衛星在中國廣袤的西部沙漠和綠洲城鎮上空盤旋。<br />\n<br />\n當天拍攝的照片顯示，這裡只是一片人跡罕至的灰白色荒漠。<br />\n<br />\n這個調查開始的地方不同尋常，它涉及其中一個我們這個時代最緊迫的人權問題。<br />\n<br />\n2018年4月22日，即在三年不到的時間裡，同一片沙漠上空拍攝的衛星照片顯示了一些新的東西。<br />\n<br />\n一個面積巨大、保安嚴密的建築呈現在眼前。<br />\n<br />\n它的外牆長約兩公里，四周矗立著16座瞭望塔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/resources/idt-sh/China_hidden_camps_chinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fresources%2Fidt-sh%2FChina_hidden_camps_chinese&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWrBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=b7b788ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fresources%2Fidt-sh%2FChina_hidden_camps_chinese&h=4c6ca045\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/resources/idt-sh/China_hidden_camps_chinese</a>"},{"pid":"d4bd3bbe87a0d6d92dabbfb259f63b1cec25d9d9","tid":2463646,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d277ee097e7652a491eb148322ea9d0afd173b5","tid":2463646,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}